---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Why the blog? — The Twins of the Father">
  <article class="mt-8" data-pagefind-body>
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-stone-900 leading-snug">Why the blog?</h1>
    </header>
    <div class="prose prose-stone max-w-none">
        <p>
            <em>"The twins of the father shall be visited on the son."</em>
        </p>
        <p>
            I'm an identical twin and have identical twin girls, Hannah and Lauren, born in August 2000.
        </p>
        <p>
            I often get the sense (usually as I'm trying to get them dressed in the morning) that I'm being
            made to pay for the misdeeds of my own childhood.
        </p>
        <p>
            The aim of the blog is to share the fun and gain enough perspective to avoid losing my marbles
            completely because they won't stop messing about and just <strong>PUT THOSE BLOODY TIGHTS ON!!!</strong>
        </p>
    </div>
    <footer class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-stone-200" data-pagefind-ignore>
      <nav class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-sm items-top">
        <div class="min-w-0">
            <a href="/" class="text-stone-500 hover:text-rose-600 transition-colors">
              <span class="text-xs block">&larr; All posts</span>
            </a>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
